NAME Teeth of Shartan, dam base
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Some unnatural force has confined the wild mountain stream here behind a magnificent earthenwork dam, which spans the wide gap between the snowy slopes of two mountains flanking the valley to the east and west. A few uquart trees, their branches bent to the ground under the weight of ice and snow, are scattered over this side of the dam. A steep road leads up the slope of the dam, alongside the icy water careening down the spillway.
*DESCRIPTION_END
