NUMBER 737
NAME Teeth of Shartan, Lakeside Road
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The road widens somewhat here, where a sagging guardrail of weatherbeaten wood lines the lake side of the road. Slick ice tipped with icicles hang delicately from each rail. A smooth, sheer cliff cut into the rock of the mountain rises from the opposite side. The magnificient peak of the Fang of Shartan looms high overhead, its sharp, broken crown looming meanacingly from its lofty, snowy brow.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 8 1567
MONSTER_GROUP 26
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
EXIT ABOVE 4
EXIT NE 738
EXIT W 736
ITEM 0 615 ADJ1=286
IFVERB recall -1
	IFVAR skill32 > 2
		ECHO PLAYER You can remember something about this being an entrance to an underground citadel, and that the opening is keyed to a phrase.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR skill32 > 4
		ECHO PLAYER You remember that the name of the place, Mirdaal, is the first part.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR skill32 > 8
		ECHO PLAYER The second part is the word 'fatha.'
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB look 0
	EQUAL abper per
	RANDOM abperroll 1 100 0
	ADD abperroll abper
	IFVAR abperroll > 175
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER Something seems a bit odd about this cliff, but you cannot quite identify what bothers you about it.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB climb 0
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You can't get any purchase on the cliff to climb it. In fact, you can't even feel the cliff at all.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR abcliffopen = 1 THEN
		ECHO PLAYER You pass through the cliff as if it wasn't even there.
		ECHO OTHERS %n disappears into the cliff face!
		MOVE 934
		AFFECT 934
		ECHO OTHERS %n just arrived, looking a bit disoriented.
		EQUAL abcliffopen 0
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Some force seems to be preventing you from entering.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 0
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER Amazingly, you can't feel anything where the cliff appears to be!
ENDIF
IFENTRY
	EQUAL abcliffopen 0
ENDIF
IFSAY Mirdaal_fatha
	ECHO PLAYER The ancient words echo back in your head like a chorus.
	EQUAL abcliffopen 1
ENDIF
